verbose_text: Therefore, the aim of the present study was to investigate the mechanisms responsible for the pro angiogenic effects of arnebin-1 on human umbilical vein endothelial cells (HUVECs), as well as those responsible for its healing effects on wounds of rats with alloxan induced diabetes mellitus (DM).
